en_861960_0	7 SLNG troops of the Security Force HQ in Kilinochchi immediately attended to a repair on the Maradam Kulam tank bund after villagers brought its possible burst due to swelling rain waters in the tank on Saturday (30).
en_861960_1	Troops taking preventive measures to stop an imminent disaster repaired the leak placing sand bags and earth on the directions given by the Commander SF-KLN and the General Officer Commanding 65 Division.
en_861960_2	3 officers and 50 troops contributed to this emergency averting a major disaster.
